########################################################################################################################
# Help for jokes
########################################################################################################################
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
[CTRL + X THEN K] or  joke : display a random dev pun or joke
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Shows a random developer pun from the bundled joke list.
The language (French or English) is selected automatically from your locale ($LANG).

Override the language via nconf (CTRL+X+C) → NIXLPER_JOKE_LANG, or in ~/.config/nixlper/nixlper.conf:
  export NIXLPER_JOKE_LANG=fr   # always French
  export NIXLPER_JOKE_LANG=en   # always English
  export NIXLPER_JOKE_LANG=auto # detect from $LANG (default)
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
